name: Laeeb Inu ERC
description: Laeeb Inu a sports fantasy football league and betting dapp Features * Fantasy Football league. Description - buy tickets to enter fantasy football tournament for the World Cup where you have a budget to create a team who wins the most points by the end of the tournament to win prizes Draft Weekly tournaments for game week fixtures to win weekly competitions and prizes. * Sports Dapp Description - betting to dapp to place bets on all sporting events and competitions. * NFT dapp and collection Description - NFT dapp to mint your sports card NFT collection, buy, trade and sell NFTS to complete your collections.
